trans-unit.source: Describes the referential constraints on the relationships in a conceptual model.
trans-unit.target: 개념적 모델의 관계에 대한 참조 제약 조건을 설명합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the built-in type kind for this <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" />.
trans-unit.target: 이 <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" />의 기본 제공 형식 유형을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.BuiltInTypeKind" /> object that represents the built-in type kind for this <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" />.
trans-unit.target: 이 <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.BuiltInTypeKind" />의 기본 제공 형식 유형을 나타내는 <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" /> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the list of properties for the "from role" on which this <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" /> is defined.
trans-unit.target: 이 <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" />가 정의된 "원본 역할"의 속성 목록을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: A collection of type <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReadOnlyMetadataCollection`1" /> that contains the list of properties for "from role" on which this <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" /> is defined.
trans-unit.target: 이 <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReadOnlyMetadataCollection`1" />가 정의된 "원본 역할"의 속성 목록이 포함된 <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" /> 형식의 컬렉션입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the "from role" that takes part in this <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" />.
A <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.RelationshipEndMember" /> object that represents the "from role" that takes part in this <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" />.
Gets the list of properties for the "to role" on which this <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" /> is defined.
trans-unit.target: 이 <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" />가 정의된 "대상 역할"의 속성 목록을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: A collection of type <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReadOnlyMetadataCollection`1" /> that contains the list of properties for the "to role" on which this <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" /> is defined.
trans-unit.target: 이 <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReadOnlyMetadataCollection`1" />가 정의된 "대상 역할"의 속성 목록이 포함된 <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" /> 형식의 컬렉션입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the "to role" that takes part in this <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" />.
A <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.RelationshipEndMember" /> object that represents the "to role" that takes part in this <see cref="T:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint" />.
Returns the combination of the names of the <see cref="P:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint.FromRole" /> and the <see cref="P:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint.ToRole" />.
The combination of the names of the <see cref="P:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint.FromRole" /> and the <see cref="P:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReferentialConstraint.ToRole" />.
